# pocDjangoBasic
A basic POC in Django ( based in a TreinaWeb video - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MsUL3Pgofl4 )

## Virtual Enviroment Inicialization
python3 -m venv .venv
# To activate
source ./.venv/bin/activate
# To deactivate
deactivate

## Django Installation
pip install django

## Create a Django Project
django-admin startproject setup .

## Run the server
python3 manage.py runserver

## Create a Django App
python3 manage.py startapp todos

## Create a Django Model (run Django default migrations)
python3 manage.py migrate

## Create a migration based in a Django Model
python3 manage.py makemigrations

## Install python-decouple (to use .env)
pip install python-decouple

## Install dj-database-url (to use DATABASE_URL)
pip install dj-database-url

## Install black (code formatter)
pip install black

## Install crispy-bootstrap5 (to use crispy forms with bootstrap 5)
pip install crispy-bootstrap5

## Create a requirements.txt file
pip freeze > requirements.txt

## Install the requirements.txt file
pip install -r requirements.txt

## VSCode Extensions
Python
Python Debugger
Django
Black Formatter
SQLite Viewer
